original_title: Andy Forrester: Most of this is Baby Fat
overview: Andy Forrester's brand of off-the-wall humor has made him a fan favorite at clubs all over the country for almost 20 years. His high energy and animated comedy has landed him spots working with some of the biggest names in comedy like Louie Anderson, Jimmie “JJ” Walker, Paul Reiser, Marc Maron and many more.
title: Andy Forrester: Most of this is Baby Fat
